snippet.textDisplay:
Go, classic 🇸🇪 "Gravad lax"
1kg salmon
4 tbsp salt (non kosher, not standard I Sweden)
4 tbsp sugar
2 tesp white pepper, crushed
1 dl dill

Mix, spread out on the salmon and wait 2 days in the fridge, done. Easy
snippet.textOriginal:
Go, classic 🇸🇪 "Gravad lax"
1kg salmon
4 tbsp salt (non kosher, not standard I Sweden)
4 tbsp sugar
2 tesp white pepper, crushed 
1 dl dill

Mix, spread out on the salmon and wait 2 days in the fridge, done. Easy
